all that measuring for?

251
00:15:22,291 --> 00:15:25,382
Eh? Oh, we always do this,
Miss Spencer.

252
00:15:25,458 --> 00:15:27,424
You'd be amazed
how often it pays off.

253
00:15:27,491 --> 00:15:30,423
