262
00:16:04,824 --> 00:16:06,756
Here, are all your staff like this?

263
00:16:06,824 --> 00:16:09,756
That's the trouble.
I can't get any decent help these days.

264
00:16:09,824 --> 00:16:11,660
God's laughing, of course.

265
00:16:11,700 --> 00:16:13,960
All he has to do
is raise his little finger,

266
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:18,400
he's got a thousand sycophantic,
prissy angels at his beck and call.

267
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:20,987
I'm lumbered with Anger and Sloth.

268
00:16:21,057 --> 00:16:24,148
Wake up, you lazy, legal layabout!

269
00:16:24,224 --> 00:16:26,815
Get up! Wake up!

270
00:16:29,924 --> 00:16:32,220
Here, well,
this is Stanley Moon.

271
00:16:32,291 --> 00:16:36,223
He is selling me his soul, and I want you
to witness it on this document.

272
00:16:36,291 --> 00:16:38,223
I want you to do some writing.

273
00:16:38,291 --> 00:16:40,416
That's your forte, isn't it? Writing.

274
00:16:40,492 --> 00:16:43,424
