T, H.

280
00:16:56,700 --> 00:17:00,018
Right. Very nice.
Now it's your turn.

281
00:17:02,425 --> 00:17:04,357
There's just one thing, though.

282
00:17:04,425 --> 00:17:06,560
-You're not having second thoughts, are you?
-No.

283
00:17:06,600 --> 00:17:10,360
-But shouldn't I sign in blood?
-Blimey, you are a traditionalist.

284
00:17:10,600 --> 00:17:12,324
All right then.

285
00:17:12,392 --> 00:17:14,449
Let's use some of his.
He'll never notice.

286
00:17:16,158 --> 00:17:18,147
