322
00:19:05,758 --> 00:19:07,600
Julie Andrews.

323
00:19:07,891 --> 00:19:10,823
I could stand
and watch them for hours.

324
00:19:10,891 --> 00:19:12,880
They've such beautiful hands.

325
00:19:12,958 --> 00:19:15,390
Such fantastic delicacy, you see.

326
00:19:15,458 --> 00:19:20,719
But combined as well
with this almost preternatural strength.

327
00:19:20,791 --> 00:19:24,587
Doesn't it make you sad
to see animals caged up like this?

328
00:19:25,758 --> 00:19:27,690
Well, in a way, but...

329
00:19:27,758 --> 00:19:30,690
