no worse off than most of us.

330
00:19:30,758 --> 00:19:32,690
How do you mean?

331
00:19:32,758 --> 00:19:35,190
Well, metaphorically speaking,

332
00:19:35,258 --> 00:19:39,190
and in a very real sense,
society creates its own cages.

333
00:19:39,258 --> 00:19:41,190
You know, cages of the mind.

334
00:19:41,258 --> 00:19:42,960
Yes. Yes.

335
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:45,190
A curious kind of cerebral captivity.

336
00:19:45,258 --> 00:19:47,190
Buy a flower, madam?

337
00:19:47,258 --> 00:19:50,781
-Oh! What's it for?
-Depraved criminals.

338
00:19:50,858 --> 00:19:56,517
You see, civilisation
has had the effect of

339
00:19:56,591 --> 00:20:01,057
inhibiting our deepest,
natural animal instincts, you see.

340
00:20:03,125 --> 00:20:05,250
The conventions of an ordered society

341
