343
00:20:12,624 --> 00:20:15,056
Must have been a marvellous man.

344
00:20:15,125 --> 00:20:17,818
Oh, yes. One of the seminal forces.

345
00:20:17,891 --> 00:20:22,323
As Rousseau said,
we must learn to unlearn

346
00:20:22,392 --> 00:20:27,324
because only by unlearning
