for ourselves, you know.

357
00:20:54,591 --> 00:20:59,023
Brahms! I can't believe it!
You too?

358
00:21:00,300 --> 00:21:02,700
Absolutely adore him.

359
00:21:02,800 --> 00:21:07,456
He has a virile romanticism
that I find irresistible.

360
00:21:07,524 --> 00:21:10,957
Oh, Brahms is just so fantastic!

361
