363
00:21:17,091 --> 00:21:19,852
-Would you like a little taste of him now then?
-Please!

364
00:21:19,924 --> 00:21:21,856
Not that I'm tense
or anything.

365
00:21:21,924 --> 00:21:24,900
It's just that it would
make me even less tense.

366
00:21:42,358 --> 00:21:44,347
Go on.

367
00:21:46,358 --> 00:21:48,381
Lie down.

368
00:21:48,458 --> 00:21:50,014
Oh, I didn't meanâ

369
00:21:52,392 --> 00:21:54,324
Let it happen.

370
00:22:19,591 --> 00:22:23,354
I love the way
he brings the flute in there.

371
00:22:23,425 --> 00:22:25,856
That is a French horn, actually.

372
00:22:25,924 --> 00:22:27,856
Oh. How silly of me.

373
00:22:27,924 --> 00:22:30,356
Oh, no, no, no, no.
Goodness gracious.

374
00:22:30,425 --> 00:22:33,686
The French horn can sound
incredibly like a flute, you know.

375
00:22:33,758 --> 00:22:38,500
In fact, not many people notice
the flute-like qualities of a French horn.

376
00:22:41,657 --> 00:22:44,800
It's so sensual and evocative.

377
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:50,300
One can almost see the trees
