than the air that surrounds it.

399
00:23:58,524 --> 00:24:00,457
Fahrenheit, of course.

400
00:24:02,791 --> 00:24:04,780
Do you like feeling things?

401
00:24:06,158 --> 00:24:09,386
Oh, yes,
I'm a very tactile person.

402
00:24:09,458 --> 00:24:11,390
I love touching things.

403
00:24:11,458 --> 00:24:13,260
Sometimes

404
00:24:13,300 --> 00:24:17,060
I go into the forest
and shut my eyes

405
00:24:17,100 --> 00:24:21,981
and just wander around touching trees
and grass and boulders.

406
00:24:22,058 --> 00:24:23,460
