410
00:24:46,024 --> 00:24:48,649
Oh, now feel something soft.

411
00:24:50,924 --> 00:24:54,049
Oh, my goodness, gracious me.

412
00:24:54,125 --> 00:24:57,114
Oh, it's unbelievable.

413
00:24:58,291 --> 00:25:00,654
Oh, the contrast.

414
00:25:00,724 --> 00:25:03,656
I've never felt anything
so exciting in my life.

415
00:25:03,724 --> 00:25:07,350
Yeah. I love it. Feel my tie.

416
00:25:15,924 --> 00:25:18,200
Oh. It's delicious!

417
00:25:18,500 --> 00:25:21,760
It's Velvet, it's so wild.

418
00:25:21,800 --> 00:25:24,000
It really does something to me.

419
00:25:28,524 --> 00:25:31,752
