but if you were a girl,

440
00:26:37,691 --> 00:26:39,680
which, of course, you are,

441
00:26:41,258 --> 00:26:45,486
and if I were a man, which,
for argument's sake, let's say I am,

442
00:26:45,557 --> 00:26:49,046
and I wanted to touch you, well...

443
00:26:49,125 --> 00:26:51,057
I wouldn't feel restrained.

444
00:26:51,125 --> 00:26:53,057
