454
00:27:15,758 --> 00:27:17,452
The Cinzano. The zoo.

455
00:27:17,524 --> 00:27:20,150
The music. The touching.

456
00:27:20,225 --> 00:27:22,656
And you're so right
about the animals.

457
00:27:22,724 --> 00:27:24,883
